
Android Battery App: Triggers alarm when fully charged
This Battery app shows features like the Battery level in percentage, the voltage the battery supplies, its temperature, its type, its health and whether it is charging or discharging.

So whats new??  

This Battery app triggers an alarm whenever your battery level goes less than 5% and also when the battery gets fully charged. Not only this!

It also sends notification on the main screen asking the user to take the necessary action. It works on every android device and very easy to use.

Moreover, the app will also prevent excessive charging of the battery, overheating and will last longer. 
